41
00:02:34,610 --> 00:02:35,650
Stop drinking.

42
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,090
Just say what you want to say.

43
00:02:42,050 --> 00:02:42,770
Princess,

44
00:02:43,810 --> 00:02:44,610
I...

45
00:02:45,690 --> 00:02:47,410
