46
00:02:49,090 --> 00:02:50,000
What favor?

47
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,160
Help me seek revenge.

48
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:55,930
Revenge?

49
00:02:57,690 --> 00:03:00,380
[Fortress Qingfeng]

50
00:02:59,010 --> 00:03:00,170
Five years ago,

51
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,920
