52
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:06,610
I grew up in Jimao Mountain since I was a child.

53
00:03:06,970 --> 00:03:08,770
Eighty percent of Jimao Mountain and its surroundings

54
00:03:08,770 --> 00:03:11,400
is mountain, and twenty percent is field.

55
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:15,220
The grain harvested throughout the year

56
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,329
