57
00:03:18,090 --> 00:03:19,950
for the people in the stronghold.

58
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:23,650
But those corrupt officials from the government

59
00:03:24,250 --> 00:03:25,910
didn't care about this at all.

60
00:03:26,690 --> 00:03:28,890
They kept coming to demand taxes.

61
